athetyādi | gāḍheneti sātiśayapīḍanena | devi devīti | sattvārthaṃ pratyekābhiprāyeṇātimahāpremnā dviruktiḥ | ramyaṃ kamanīyatvāt | rahasyaṃ gopanīyatvāt śrāvakādidharmapravṛtteṣu | sāraṃ pāramitāmahāyānoktaṃ tattvaṃ tasmād api sārataraṃ śreṣṭhaṃ | sarvabuddhair iti vajrasattvanirmitair dīpaṃkarādibhiḥ samyaksaṃbuddhaiḥ ||
